events.title: the friends break into Skywalker Ranch and get to watch The Phantom Menace

movie.title: Fanboys
movie.plot: Star Wars fanatics take a cross-country trip to George Lucas' Skywalker Ranch so their dying friend can see a screening of Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace (1999) before its release.
